<p>cd进入openssl源码目录</p>
<p>执行 <code>perl Configure VC-WIN64A no-asm no-shared --prefix=&quot;D:\Project\opensslwork\openssl\build&quot; --openssldir=&quot;D:\Project\opensslwork\openssl\build\ssl&quot;</code></p>
